WorkItem.Description: Today I updated Wabbitemu TI-84 Plus Silver Edition on Windows 7, 64 bit. The calculator immediately stopped working (screen is blank and will not turn on). I tried uninstalling and reinstalling and the calculator does not work. I love Wabbitemu and would really appreciate if anyone could help me get it working again!

Comments.Message:
Hi,

Thank you to tech support who helped me resolve this issue so rapidly! Here is what they suggested I try doing:

"Try resizing Wabbitemu. You can do so by dragging from any corner of the window. If that does not work, try turning on Wabbitemu from the debug menu."

I was able to resolve this issue by resizing the Wabbitemu window. Thank you tech support!
